\c 31
\s UJakobe ubalekela uLabani
\p
\v 1 Wasesizwa amazwi amadodana kaLabani esithi: UJakobe uthethe konke okukababa; langalokho okwakungokukababa wenza lonke loludumo\x + Hlab. 49.16.\x*.
\v 2 UJakobe wasebona ubuso bukaLabani\x + 4.5.\x*, futhi khangela, babunganjengamandulo\f + \fk mandulo: \fl Heb. \fq izolo lakuthangi.\f* kuye.
\v 3 IN\sc KOSI\sc* yasisithi kuJakobe: Buyela elizweni laboyihlo lezihlotsheni zakho; njalo ngizakuba lawe\x + 31.13; 28.15; 32.9.\x*.
\v 4 UJakobe wasethuma wababiza oRasheli loLeya emadlelweni emhlanjini wakhe,
\v 5 wathi kibo: Ngiyabona ubuso bukayihlo\x + 31.2.\x* ukuthi kabunjengamandulo kimi; kodwa uNkulunkulu kababa ube lami\x + 31.3.\x*.
\v 6 Futhi lina liyazi ukuthi ngamandla ami wonke ngimsebenzele uyihlo\x + 31.38-40; 30.29.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa uyihlo ungikhohlisile, waphendula iholo lami okwezikhathi ezilitshumi\x + 31.41. Nani 14.22. Neh. 4.12. Jobe 19.3. Zek. 8.23. Isa. 4.1. Mat. 18.21.\x*, kanti uNkulunkulu kamvumelanga ukwenza okubi kimi.
\v 8 Kwathi esitsho njalo: Ezilamabala zizakuba liholo lakho, khona umhlambi wonke wazala ezilamabala. Kwathi esitsho njalo: Ezingamaqamule zizakuba liholo lakho, khona umhlambi wonke wazala ezingamaqamule\x + 30.32.\x*.
\v 9 Ngokunjalo uNkulunkulu uthethe izifuyo zikayihlo, wanginika\x + 31.1.\x*.
\v 10 Kwasekusithi, ngesikhathi umhlambi umitha, ngaphakamisa amehlo ami ngabona ephutsheni, khangela-ke, izimpongo ezikhwela umhlambi zazingamaqamule, zilamabala, lezizinala.
\v 11 Ingilosi kaNkulunkulu yasisithi kimi ephutsheni: Jakobe! Ngathi: Khangela, ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 12 Yasisithi: Ake uphakamise amehlo akho ubone, zonke impongo ezikhwela umhlambi zingamaqamule, zilamabala lezizinala\x + Eks. 9.18.\x*; ngoba ngibonile konke uLabani akwenze kuwe\x + Eks. 3.7.\x*.
\v 13 NginguNkulunkulu weBhetheli lapho owagcoba khona insika, owathembisa khona isithembiso kimi\x + 28.18-20.\x*. Khathesi, vuka, uphume kulelilizwe, ubuyele elizweni lokuzalwa kwakho\x + 31.3; 32.9.\x*.
\v 14 ORasheli loLeya baphendula bathi kuye: Siselesabelo lelifa endlini kababa yini?
\v 15 Kasibalwa \add nje\add*ngabezizwe kuye yini? Ngoba wasithengisa, lokudla wazidlela futhi imali yethu\x + 29.15,20,27.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba inotho yonke uNkulunkulu ayemuke ubaba ingeyethu leyabantwana bethu; khathesi-ke, konke uNkulunkulu akutsho kuwe, kwenze.
\p
\v 17 UJakobe wasesukuma, wakhweza amadodana akhe labomkakhe emakameleni;
\v 18 waqhuba izifuyo zakhe zonke, layo impahla yakhe yonke abeyizuzile, izifuyo ayelazo, ayezizuze ePadani-Arama, ukuze aye kuIsaka uyise elizweni leKhanani.
\v 19 Njalo uLabani esehambile ukuyagunda izimvu zakhe, uRasheli weba izithombe\f + \fk izithombe: \fl Heb. \fq amatherafi.\f* uyise ayelazo.
\v 20 UJakobe wasuka enyenya engananzelelwe\f + \fk engananzelelwe: \fl Heb. \fq inhliziyo kaLabani.\f* kuLabani umSiriya, ngoba kamazisanga ukuthi uyabaleka.
\v 21 Wasebaleka, yena lakho konke ayelakho, wasukuma, wachapha umfula, wakhangelisa ubuso bakhe\x + 2 Kho. 12.17. Luka 9.51.\x* entabeni yeGileyadi.
\p
\v 22 Kwasekusaziswa uLabani ngosuku lwesithathu ukuthi uJakobe ubalekile.
\v 23 Wasethatha abafowabo kanye laye, waxotshana laye ibanga lensuku eziyisikhombisa, wamfica entabeni yeGileyadi.
\v 24 UNkulunkulu wasesiza kuLabani umSiriya ephutsheni lebusuku\x + 20.3.\x*, wathi kuye: Ziqaphele, hlezi ukhulume loJakobe okuhle kumbe okubi\f + \fk okuhle kumbe okubi: \fl Heb. \fq kusukela kukuhle kusiya kokubi.\f*.
\v 25 ULabani wasemfica uJakobe. Njalo uJakobe wayemise ithente lakhe entabeni; uLabani laye kanye labafowabo bamisa entabeni yeGileyadi.
\v 26 ULabani wasesithi kuJakobe: Wenzeni, ukuthi usuke unyenye ngingananzelele\x + 31.20,27.\x*, uthathe amadodakazi ami ngamandla njengabathunjiweyo ngenkemba\x + 1 Sam. 30.2.\x*?
\v 27 Ubalekeleni ngasese, unginyenyela\f + \fk unginyenyela: \fl Heb. \fq ungeba.\f*, ungangazisanga, ukuthi ngabe ngikuvalelise ngokuthokoza langengoma, ngesigubhu langechacho?
\v 28 Njalo kawungivumelanga ukuthi ngange\x + 31.55. Ruthe 1.9,14. 1 Kho. 19.20. Seb. 20.37.\x* amadodana ami lamadodakazi ami. Khathesi wenze ubuthutha\x + 1 Sam. 26.21.\x* ngokwenza \add lokho\add*.
\v 29 Kusemandleni esandla sami ukwenza okubi kini; kodwa uNkulunkulu kayihlo\x + 31.42; 28.13.\x* ukhulumile kimi ebusuku obudlulileyo\x + 31.24,29; 19.34.\x* wathi: Ziqaphele ukuthi ungakhulumi loJakobe okuhle kumbe okubi.
\v 30 Khathesi-ke, ukuhamba uhambile, ngoba ngokukhanuka ukhanukile indlu kayihlo; webeleni onkulunkulu bami\x + 31.19. Hlu. 18.24.\x*?
\v 31 UJakobe wasephendula wathi kuLabani: Ngoba ngesaba, ngoba wathi: Hlezi ungihluthunele amadodakazi akho.
\v 32 Lowo ozathola kuye onkulunkulu bakho kangaphili; phambi kwabafowethu zinanzelelele okukimi, uzithathele. Ngoba uJakobe wayengazi ukuthi uRasheli wayebebile.
\v 33 ULabani wasengena ethenteni likaJakobe lethenteni likaLeya, lethenteni lezincekukazi ezimbili, kodwa katholanga. Waphuma ethenteni likaLeya, wangena ethenteni likaRasheli.
\v 34 Kodwa uRasheli wayethethe izithombe, wazifaka esikhwameni sesihlalo sekamela, wahlala phezu kwazo. ULabani waphumphutha ithente lonke kodwa katholanga.
\v 35 Wasesithi kuyise: Kalungavuthi \add ulaka\add* emehlweni enkosi yami ukuthi ngingesukume phambi kwakho\x + Levi 19.32.\x*, ngoba indlela yabesifazana ikimi. Wabhudula, kodwa kazitholanga izithombe.
\p
\v 36 UJakobe wasethukuthela, waphikisana loLabani; uJakobe waphendula wathi kuLabani: Isiphambeko sami siyini, isono sami siyini, ukuthi ungixotshe ngokutshiseka\x + Lam. 4.19.\x*?
\v 37 Njengoba usubambabambe kuyo impahla yami yonke, utholeni okwayo impahla yonke yendlu yakho? Ibeke lapha phambi kwabafowethu\x + 31.54.\x* labafowenu\x + 31.23.\x* ukuze baqume phakathi kwethu sobabili.
\v 38 Iminyaka le engamatshumi amabili ngangilawe; izimvukazi zakho lezibhuzikazi zakho kaziphunzanga, lezinqama zemihlambi yakho kangizidlanga.
\v 39 Ezadatshulwayo kangizilethanga kuwe, mina ngazihlawula; esandleni sami wazibiza, zebiwe emini loba zebiwe ebusuku\x + Eks. 22.12.\x*.
\v 40 Ngangi\add njalo\add* emini imbalela yangidla, lamakhaza ebusuku, ubuthongo babaleka emehlweni ami.
\v 41 Iminyaka le engamatshumi amabili bengisemzini wakho, ngakusebenzela okweminyaka elitshumi lane ngenxa yamadodakazi akho amabili\x + 29.27,28.\x*, leminyaka eyisithupha ngenxa yomhlambi wakho; njalo waphendula iholo lami okwezikhathi ezilitshumi\x + 31.7.\x*.
\v 42 Ngaphandle kokuthi uNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 124.1,2.\x* kababa, uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama loKwesaba kukaIsaka\x + 31.53.\x* ubengelami, isibili khathesi ubuzangixotsha ngize. Inhlupheko zami lomtshikatshika wezandla zami uNkulunkulu ubonile\x + 29.32.\x*, wa\add ku\add*sola\x + 1 Lan. 12.17.\x* izolo ebusuku\x + 31.29.\x*.
\s Isivumelwano sikaJakobe loLabani
\p
\v 43 ULabani wasephendula wathi kuJakobe: Amadodakazi angamadodakazi ami, lamadodana angamadodana ami, lomhlambi ngumhlambi wami, lakho konke okubonayo kungokwami; lemadodakazini ami ngizakwenzani kuwo lamuhla, loba kubantwana bawo abawazeleyo?
\v 44 Khathesi-ke, woza, asenze isivumelwano\x + 26.28.\x*, mina lawe, njalo sibe yibufakazi phakathi kwami lawe\x + 31.48. Josh. 24.27.\x*.
\v 45 UJakobe wasethatha ilitshe, walimisa laba yinsika\x + 28.18.\x*.
\v 46 UJakobe wasesithi kubafowabo: Buthani amatshe. Basebethatha amatshe, benza inqumbi; badla khona phezu kwenqumbi.
\v 47 ULabani waseyibiza \add ngokuthi\add* yiJegari-Sahadutha\f + \fk iJegari-Sahadutha: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq inqumbi yobufakazi.\f*, kodwa uJakobe wayibiza \add ngokuthi\add* yiGaledi\f + \fk iGaledi: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq inqumbi yobufakazi.\f*.
\v 48 ULabani wasesithi: Linqwaba iyibufakazi phakathi kwami lawe lamuhla\x + 31.44.\x*. Ngakho bayitha ibizo layo iGaledi,
\v 49 leMizipa\x + Hlu. 11.29,34.\x*\f + \fk iMizipa: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq inqaba yokulinda.\f*, ngoba wathi: IN\sc KOSI\sc* kayilinde phakathi kwami lawe, lapho singabonani omunye lomunye.
\v 50 Uba uhlupha amadodakazi ami, njalo uba uthatha abafazi phezu kwamadodakazi ami, kakulamuntu olathi, bona, uNkulunkulu ungumfakazi phakathi kwami lawe.
\v 51 ULabani wasesithi kuJakobe: Khangela linqwaba, khangela-ke lensika engiyiphosileyo phakathi kwami lawe.
\v 52 Linqwaba kayibe yibufakazi, lensika kayibe yibufakazi\x + 31.44,48.\x*, bokuthi mina kangiyikuyidlula linqwaba ngiye kuwe, lawe kawuyikuyidlula linqwaba lalinsika uze kimi ngokubi.
\v 53 UNkulunkulu kaAbrahama loNkulunkulu kaNahori, kahlulele phakathi kwethu, uNkulunkulu kayise wabo. UJakobe wasefunga ngoKwesaba kukayise uIsaka\x + 31.42.\x*.
\v 54 UJakobe wasehlaba umhlatshelo entabeni, wabiza abafowabo ukuthi badle isinkwa\x + 31.37.\x*; basebesidla isinkwa, balala entabeni.
\v 55 ULabani wasevuka ekuseni kakhulu, wanga amadodana akhe lamadodakazi akhe\x + 31.28,43.\x*, wawabusisa\x + 28.1.\x*; uLabani wasehamba wabuyela endaweni yakhe.
